parameters:
There's no point in returning to the surface. We must head
underground.

What is this creature? It's so bizarre... A tentacle
monster?

Whoa? They're gathering! They don't seem to want to let us
pass, do they?
Defeat them with a normal attack \c[27]【H Event】\c[0]
Wipe them out with a battle skill
普通の攻撃で倒す\c[27]【Ｈイベント】\c[0]

It's not worth using my battle skills. I'll finish this with
my hand chop! Take this!

Wha-wha...!? What the heck!? Were they on the ceiling too!?
Let go! Let go of me!?

--Masaki was restrained by the writhing tentacles and had
her clothes torn off!

You lustful curs! Getting so carried away! I'll wipe you all
out at once!

--The writhing tentacles were charred to a crisp and
vanished!

...Seriously, what a waste of time. I need to regroup with
the others quickly--
戦技で一網打尽にする

Hmph! Even in large numbers, you're just easy prey! Taste my
sorcery! Heavenly Thunderbolt--!

--The writhing tentacles were charred to a crisp and
vanished!

Ha ha ha! You picked the wrong opponent! Now, let's move on
to regroup with everyone!
Are these the war demons we've defeated before?

No! These are not the individuals themselves. They're
vengeful ghosts.

Amplifying the grudges of the dead to create malevolent
spirits--it's a forbidden secret technique from the Heian
period. I see, so that's Gyoun's true nature!

You bastards... By the order of Lord Gyoun, we shall kill
you here...!
~~~~h! (They're even manipulating the dead to fight us!? )

To have to defeat an opponent we've already killed once...
What an unpleasant battle.

When one dies, they all become Buddha... To think even those
who became Buddha would do such atrocities...

To use those who were once allies as pawns after their
death... Truly a ruthless and fearsome enemy.

Gyoun--I won't forgive that man! I'll smash the Divine
Threefold Sword into his head!
Uwahh!? It's starting to shake again!
Such a tremendous tremor...! I can't stand up!
The exit is just ahead, hurry everyone!

--Stamina and skill power have been \c[24]fully
restored\c[0]!
